data.description: Welcome, new front steps take you up to a spacious front porch. Lovely Foyer greets you. This home has old world grand style, mixed with modern updates! Large living room with bay window flows into dining room, and huge updated kitchen 2021 featuring tons of cabinets and lighting and stainless appliances 2020. Updated electrical 2021, with USB outlets!  Ultra-high ceilings and Harwood floors throughout! Tons of storage and closets! Beautiful ornate banister and stunning staircase. Tons of decorative details to the home. Upstairs big full bath and 3 large beds with new ceiling fans.  Large mud/ four seasons room at the back entrance. 2.5 car garage with newer siding, very private backyard with fencing and new steps 2023. Half bath on first floor!  Furnace 2005. Water tank 2021. Security system and smart home tech is present, just sign up! Waterproofed basement has glass block windows, sump,  and washer/dryer. More storage! Close to Ohio City, Detroit Shore way, Highways, Hospitals, dining and shopping!  Please enjoy our attached video tour !
